\c 266 

\s VILIMA VIOTE NA MABONDE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Vilima viote na mabonde vitayeyushwa, Neno lake Bwana imara litasimama.\bd*
\pc \bdit Simama imara ulilinde, Neno lake Bwana imara, kesha kila siku uombe utasimama.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Bwana Yesu atapako kuja tutamuona, Neno lake Bwana imara litasimama.\bd*
\pc \bdit Simama imara ulilinde, Neno lake Bwana imara, kesha kila siku uombe utasimama.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Sisi wote tuwe tayari kua kuongojea, Atujuwe siku wala saa Bwana Atarudi.\bd*
\pc \bdit Simama imara ulilinde, Neno lake Bwana imara, kesha kila siku uombe utasimama.\bdit*
